</code></pre>

users/invitation_rejected_subject.txt <pre><code>    Invitation has been rejected
</code></pre> users/invitation_rejected_message.txt <pre><code>    Hello!

    The following invitation has been rejected.

    Full name: {{ invitation.full_name }}

    Target: {{ name }} {{ type }}

    Role: {{ role }}
</code></pre> users/invitation_rejected_message.html <pre><code>    &lt;html&gt;
    &lt;head lang="en"&gt;
        &lt;meta charset="UTF-8"&gt;
