</code></pre>

booking/notification_subject.txt <pre><code>    Reminder about upcoming booking.
</code></pre> booking/notification_message.txt <pre><code>    Hello!

    Please do not forget about upcoming booking:
    {% for resource in resources %}
        {{ resource.name }}{% if not forloop.last %}, {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}.
</code></pre> booking/notification_message.html <pre><code>    &lt;html&gt;
    &lt;head lang="en"&gt;
        &lt;meta charset="UTF-8"&gt;
