marketplace/notification_about_project_ending_subject.txt <pre><code>    {% if count_projects &gt; 1 %}Your {{ count_projects }} projects{% else %} Project{% endif %} will be deleted on {{ end_date|date:'d/m/Y' }}.
</code></pre> marketplace/notification_about_project_ending_message.txt <pre><code>    Hello {{ user.full_name }}!

    The following projects are ending {% if delta == 1 %} tomorrow {% else %} in {{ delta }} days{% endif %}:

    {% for project in projects %}
        - {{ project.name }} ({{ project.url }})
    {% endfor %}

